{
  "texts": [
    "Remote patient monitoring is very prevalent these days, and protecting the privacy of enormous volumes of data is a major challenge with such systems [5].",
    "These issues can be solved with several technologies, such as Mobile Edge Computing (MEC), Fog Computing, and Blockchain [6].",
    "Blockchain technology is being explored as a potential solution for addressing security challenges.",
    "This has led to increased interest in using blockchain to safeguard sensitive data [3].",
    "Integration of IoT-based eHealth systems using blockchain technology is presented in lots of research, and many challenges are faced in this integration."
  ]
}